Use the standard library
This is how to ceil of x:
   Remember that i is toint of x
   When tofloat of i is less than x, then:
      The answer is sum of i and 1
   End when
   The answer is i
Now you know

This is how to sum_squares of arr:
   Remember that total is 0
   Remember that n is arr's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that x is item i in arr
      Remember that y is ceil of x
      Remember that total is sum of total and (product of y and y)
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is total
Now you know